@ImageProcessor.Api_HostAddress = http://localhost:5084

### Health Check
GET {{ImageProcessor.Api_HostAddress}}/api/Image/health

### Upload and Process Image (Thumbnail)
POST {{ImageProcessor.Api_HostAddress}}/api/Image/upload
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="sample.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./sample-image.jpg
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="operation"

GenerateThumbnails
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="parameters[size]"

200
--boundary--

### Resize Image Job
POST {{ImageProcessor.Api_HostAddress}}/api/Image/resize
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "imagePath": "uploads/sample.jpg",
  "outputPath": "processed/resized_sample.jpg",
  "width": 800,
  "height": 600,
  "maintainAspectRatio": true
}

### Apply Filters Job
POST {{ImageProcessor.Api_HostAddress}}/api/Image/apply-filters
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "imagePath": "uploads/sample.jpg",
  "outputPath": "processed/filtered_sample.jpg",
  "filters": ["Grayscale", "Sepia"]
}

### Generate Thumbnail Job
POST {{ImageProcessor.Api_HostAddress}}/api/Image/thumbnail
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "imagePath": "uploads/sample.jpg",
  "outputPath": "processed/thumb_sample.jpg",
  "size": 150
}

### Batch Processing Job
POST {{ImageProcessor.Api_HostAddress}}/api/Image/batch
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "imagePaths": [
    "uploads/image1.jpg",
    "uploads/image2.jpg",
    "uploads/image3.jpg"
  ],
  "outputDirectory": "processed/batch",
  "operation": "GenerateThumbnails",
  "parameters": {
    "size": 200
  }
}

### Trigger Cleanup Job
POST {{ImageProcessor.Api_HostAddress}}/api/Image/cleanup

### Get Job Status
GET {{ImageProcessor.Api_HostAddress}}/api/Image/status/{{jobId}}

### Access Hangfire Dashboard
GET {{ImageProcessor.Api_HostAddress}}/hangfire

